3   Ore Yudas ilo oitarasayie pee edol ajo eidipaki aaiguanare, neitoki ainosu neshuku nena pisai tomoni uni e nkosholai ashukoki ilapolosak kituaak o lpayiani, 
4  ejo, “Aitarruoyie aitarasayie oltung'ani lemeeta entiyoto metari.” Kake etiaakita ninche, “Ainyoo natii ninche iyiook? Iyie ine.” 
5  Nenang'aki nena pisai e nkosholai atua enkaji e Nkai neipung; nelo agor kewan. 
6  Nedumu ilapolosak nena pisai enkosholai nejo, “Mebara ti nikipik olbene le Nkai amu osarge einosieki.” 
7  Neiguana te nebo neinyiang'unye enkurma o laitobirani loo motioo pee enukarieki iltung'ana leeiking'a. 
8  Enkaraki e ina pee eji ina kurma, enkurma o sarge o taata. 
9   Ina kata eitabayioki ina natejo oloiboni le Nkai oji Yeremia pee ejo, “Neya ninche impisai tomoni uni e nkosholai nainosieki ilo otudung'oki enkinyiang'a, otudung'okito enkinyiang'a lkulikae ayiok le Israel. 
10  Neishooyo aainosie enkurma o laitobirani loo motioo anaa enaaitanapa nanu Olaitoriani.”

