11  Neitasheyieki Yesu te dukuya olbalusui neikilikuan olbalusui ninye ajoki, “Aa ira iyie olaiguanani loo Lyahudi?” Nejoki Yesu, “Iyie ojo.” 
12  Ore pee eitang'or ilapolosak kituaak o lpayiani, neitu hoo ewaliki. 
13  Nejoki Pilato, “Ai mining eneba imbaa nikinteenikini?” 
14  Kake eitu ewaliki te mbae hoo nabo, o meing'asiayu olbalusui oleng.

