15  Naa ore apa ake to sirua le Pasaka, naa kelaaki olbalusui esiamo oltung'ani obo oena anaa oloyieu ninche.


16  Netii ina kata oltung'ani obo yioloti te nkarruisho oena oji Barabas. 
17  Ore pee etumo, nejoki Pilato ninche, “Kalo iyieuu nalaaki intae? Ai Barabas anaa Yesu oji Kristo?” 
18  Amu eyiolo ajo to lom eishooitie ninye. 
19  Ore pee eton Pilato to lorika le nkiguana neirriwaki enkitok enye olkilikuai ajoki, “Toduaa miaas ae te ilo tung'ani lemeeta entiyoto amu atanyamala duoo too mbaa kumok te nkidetidet te nkaraki ninye.” 
20  Kake etukurrakita ilapolosak kituaak o lpayiani lolorere metoomonu Barabas, neishooyo Yesu metaari. 
21  Neitoki ake olbalusui ajoki ninche, “Kaing'ae te kulo pokira aare iyieuu nalaaki intae?” Nejo, “Barabas.” 
22  Nejoki Pilato, “Kaa naa aitaas Yesu oji Kristo?” Nejoki pooki, “Inchooi metashei.” 
23  Nejo, “Aainyo, kaa torroni etaasa ninye?” Neitoki aaitulusoo aabuak aajo, “Inchoo metashei.” 
24   Ore pee edol Pilato ajo meeta ae naidim ataasa, kake keponari ake oloilole nedumu enkare, neisuj inkaik te dukuya olorere nejo, “Maata taa nanu entiyoto to sarge lele tung'ani eng'urai maate ena bae.” 
25  Newal iltung'ana pooki aajo, “Inchoo osarge lenye meeu shumata iyiook o nkera ang.” 
26  Nelaaki te ina kata Barabas; neari Yesu too nkeenta, neishori metashei.


27  Nerik isikarini lo lbalusui Yesu atua enkaji o lbalusui naji Praitorio neiturrurrokinote oltim pooki. 
28  Neoru nkilani enyena neishopoki olkila onyokie. 
29  Neshetu olmarisian loo lkiku nepik elukunya enye, nepik entiyani enkaina enye e tatene, negilaki kung aakueniyie nejoki, “Supa olaiguanani loo Lyahudi!” 
30  Nenotaki ninye neoru ina tiyani naibung'ita, neoshioshie endukuya enye. 
31  Ore pee eidip aatakueniyie, neoru olkila onyokie neishopoki nkilani enyena, nerik ninye aapuo aashe.

