32  Ore epuku aapuo neinepu oltung'ani le Kirene oji Simon nearaki ninye pee enap osalaba. 
33  Ore pee ebaiki ewueji neji Golgata, aa keji ewueji e mborbor, 
34   neisho ninche Yesu enaisho oo sabibu naitushulakaki olodua metooko. Ore pee eishamisham neany eok. 
35   Ore pee eidip aatasho ninye, neor nkilani enyena aaoshie enkukuo. 
36  Netoni ninche aarrip ninye te ine. 
37  Nepik ele sirata shumata elukunya enye aajo “YESU ELE OLAIGUANANI LOO LYAHUDI.” 
38  Neshei te ina kata te nebo ninye ilapurrok aare, obo te nkaina e tatene, o likae te nkaina e kedienye. 
39   Nemor iloogiroo eipirripir ilukuny, aajo, 
40   “Eiyie doi ogil enkaji e Nkai nishet too nkolong'i uni, intajeu kewan; te naa iyie Enkerai e Nkai, tadou to salaba.” 
41  Neiko sii ninche neijia lapolosak o lasirak te nebo lpaiyiani ejo, 
42  “Kulikae ake eitajeu nemeidim aitejeu kewan, olaa ninye olaiguanani loo Siraeli. Inchoo taata edou to salaba pee kiruk ninye.” 
43   Ore amu Enkai etipika osiligi lenye inchoo naa eitajeu taa Enkai ninye tenaa keetayie tipat; amu etejo naa, “Ara Enkerai e Nkai!” 
44  Nemor sii lelo apurrok ootashoki te nebo o ninye.

