45  Ore pee ebaiki saa ile, nerip enaimin enkop o metabaiki saa naaudo. 
46   Ore pee ebaya saa naaudo, neishir Yesu to ltoilo sapuk ajo, “Eli, Eli, lama sabaktani?” Naa inchere, “Enkai ai, Enkai ai, aainyo pee kitung'uayie?” 
47  Ore pee ening kulikae te lelo ooitashe te ine nejo, “Eliya eipoto.” 
48   Nekuet nabo kata obo le lelo nepik osuguroi enaisho naisuijo oo sabibu neremoki eng'udi naado neisho metooko. 
49  Nejoki ilkulikae, “Tapala maing'urai te naa kelotu Eliya aitajeu.” 
50  Neitoki Yesu aishir to ltoilo sapuk, nedung'o tau.


51   Neiperra nabo kata olkarasha le nkaji e Nkai aaku are, aiteru te shumata o metabaiki abori, neikirikira enkop nedanya ndapidapo; 
52  nebolo inkuraren neitopiuni seseni kumok loo sinyat ooirurate; 
53  ore pee epuku too nkuraren eidipa Yesu atopiu, nejing ina ang sinyati neipang'aki ltung'ana kumok. 
54  Ore ilo kitok loo sikarini oorripito Yesu o lelo ootii te nebo ninye, pee edol eikirikire enkop o kulie baa naatotiwuo, neureishoyu oleng ejo, “Esipa Enkerai e Nkai ele tung'ani.”


55   Netii ine wueji inkituaak kumok naaing'orita te nelakua naatusujutua Yesu eing'uaa Galilaya eisiaaita ninye. 
56  Ore te nebo ninche etii Mariamu Magdalene o Mariamu ng'otonye Yakobo o Yosef, o ng'otonye layiok le Sebedayo.

